PUBLISHERS' NOTE.

Dr. Herbermann has thoroughly revised his Sallust—for ten years the, best edition published in this country—and, to better adapt it to young studente, has given before the text, helpful Sum- maries of Chapters. References are also given to all the leading Grammars. It is believed that in Introduction, Summaries of Chapters, Text, Notos, and VocabuZam, everything needsul has been done to adapt the book* to Secondary School use.
